WEBVTT

00:00:00.518 --> 00:00:01.879
NINETY SIX.

00:00:02.796 --> 00:00:06.097
MRS. BAKER, far vos hot ir gevolt haynt makhn dem intervyu?

00:00:07.605 --> 00:00:09.489
far vos hot ir gevolt haynt redn?

00:00:10.609 --> 00:00:12.628
vayl ikh vil di velt zol visn

00:00:13.714 --> 00:00:16.998
zi iz geven shtum biz yetst, loz zi yetst UNK epes.

00:00:18.743 --> 00:00:20.334
tsi iz es vikhtik

00:00:20.334 --> 00:00:22.044
az me zol blaybn yidn?

00:00:22.590 --> 00:00:24.238
yo, zeyer vikhtik.

00:00:25.273 --> 00:00:27.579
zol men za- darf men zayn religyez?

00:00:27.619 --> 00:00:30.363
me darf nisht zayn religyez. me darf zayn a mentsh.

00:00:31.281 --> 00:00:33.823
a religye hot gornisht tsu tun mit keyn mentshheyt.

00:00:37.018 --> 00:00:38.024
vos hot

00:00:38.048 --> 00:00:39.876
vos darfn mir oyslernen

00:00:39.876 --> 00:00:41.602
fun di ale derfarungen?

00:00:42.402 --> 00:00:44.370
vos darfn mir aroysnemen fun dem?

00:00:45.304 --> 00:00:46.833
vos meynt ir dos vos

00:00:47.177 --> 00:00:49.972
vos kenen mir lernen fun der tsveyter velt milkhome?

00:00:50.907 --> 00:00:56.824
me ken lernen az di gantse velt hot geshvign ven me hot gebrent lebedike mentshn.

00:00:59.327 --> 00:01:04.349
nisht bloyz di gantse velt, nor yidn bikhlal hobn ⟨oykh⟩ gornisht getun fun Amerike

00:01:04.693 --> 00:01:06.440
zey hobn gornisht getun. se

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:11.730
s'iz geven mentshn gekumen zogn vos me tut dort. me brent lebedike mentshn mit toyznter hi-

00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:14.036
un s'hot keyner nisht gornisht

00:01:14.430 --> 00:01:15.757
shtum geven di velt.

00:01:20.050 --> 00:01:23.419
vos vilt ir zogn tsu di kumedike doyres

00:01:23.779 --> 00:01:29.595
nisht nor tsu di eyniklekh b- ober tsu di ur eyniklekh un di kumedike doyres n- in ayer mishpokhe?

00:01:29.348 --> 00:01:32.230
ikh zog tsu mayn tokhter, ikh zog tsu mayn tokhter

00:01:32.230 --> 00:01:33.780
"ze, ZINele

00:01:34.765 --> 00:01:39.180
far vos redstu nisht yidish tsu di kinder? er iz dokh UNK, er ken nisht keyn yidish."

00:01:39.473 --> 00:01:45.544
"ikh volt" zogt zi "gelernt zey yidish, ober s'iz nishto keyn yidishe shuln lebn mir. geyn firn vayter zey iz shver."

00:01:45.544 --> 00:01:50.823
ober dos iz gut, me zol dermanen m'iz a yid, un vos UNK dos gantse lebn gelitn, un f-

00:01:51.454 --> 00:01:56.814
"mame," zogt zi, "ets hot ge- ⟨nokh⟩ gehat yidish, yidish, yidish, vos UNK folk UNK gebrengt.

00:01:56.814 --> 00:01:58.464
Hitler hot ets gebrengt?"

00:01:58.464 --> 00:01:59.770
shoyn dos entfert zi mir.

00:02:01.377 --> 00:02:03.075
tsi iz Yisroel vikhtik?

00:02:05.072 --> 00:02:08.356
s'iz gants vikhtik, s'iz do a yidish land. WHY NOT?

00:02:09.526 --> 00:02:11.360
darf men es untershtitsn?

00:02:11.063 --> 00:02:12.778
me darf im shtitsn.

00:02:13.611 --> 00:02:15.073
me shtits ⟨undzere⟩.

00:02:16.243 --> 00:02:19.578
mir shikn yedes yor f- keyn Yisroel gelt.

00:02:22.555 --> 00:02:26.329
vos trakht ir haynt funem daytshishn, funem poylishn folk?

00:02:32.123 --> 00:02:34.462
di daytshn zogn az zey veysn gornisht

00:02:34.654 --> 00:02:39.524
az m'hot undzere shvestern getribn fun lager tsu lager bay di shtetlekh daytshishe

00:02:39.524 --> 00:02:43.784
ven di DEUTSCHEN zogn UNK zenen geshtanen DEUTSCHE folk un geshpign oyf zey

00:02:44.661 --> 00:02:47.659
zenen ale a s- folk fun merders.

00:02:47.850 --> 00:02:49.751
dos zog ikh mayns, mayne ⟨kinder⟩

00:02:51.951 --> 00:02:55.370
polyakn, polyakn hobn oykh eybik ⟨derlitn fun zey⟩.

00:02:59.494 --> 00:03:01.260
vos zogt ir fun di rusn?

00:03:02.802 --> 00:03:04.973
s'rusishe folk iz a gut folk.

00:03:04.995 --> 00:03:08.094
di mentshn zenen gute. der rezhim toyg nisht.

00:03:10.463 --> 00:03:13.579
zey hobn aleyn gelitn, hobn aleyn gehungert in di krig.

00:03:13.585 --> 00:03:15.891
mir hobn mit zey in eynem gehungert.

00:03:16.555 --> 00:03:19.890
ober m'hot undz nisht gebrent. m'hot undz UNK derharget.

00:03:24.047 --> 00:03:25.765
eyder mir veln farendikn

00:03:25.765 --> 00:03:29.610
vilt ir epes tsugebn vos ir hot nokh alts nisht ibergegebn?

00:03:31.810 --> 00:03:33.373
ikh ken shoyn meyn nisht.

00:03:37.311 --> 00:03:39.903
tsu shver zikh tsu dermanen di ale zakhn.

00:03:43.639 --> 00:03:45.675
MRS. BAKER, ikh dank aykh zeyer.

00:03:46.677 --> 00:03:48.038
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

00:03:50.608 --> 00:03:51.985
ver ligt do in bild?

00:03:52.347 --> 00:03:54.113
der zeyde mit di bobe.

00:03:54.152 --> 00:03:55.715
fun ah

00:03:55.148 --> 00:03:56.863
fun di mame's eltern.

00:03:56.970 --> 00:03:58.229
vi heysn zey?

00:03:58.202 --> 00:04:01.419
er heyst Sh- hot geheysn Shmuel, un zi

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:04.034
Perele.

00:04:03.923 --> 00:04:05.942
in velkhn yor iz dos genumen gevorn?

00:04:05.998 --> 00:04:06.650
ikh veys.

00:04:08.023 --> 00:04:12.286
dos hot mir geshikt di PICTURE mayns a mume fun NEW YORK, di mame's a shvester.

00:04:12.242 --> 00:04:13.788
dos iz in Gritse?

00:04:13.731 --> 00:04:15.731
NO, in NEW YORK hot zi mir geshikt di PICTURE.

00:04:15.381 --> 00:04:17.552
NO, ⟨vu⟩ dos iz genumen gevorn?

00:04:16.882 --> 00:04:18.192
dos iz on Amshtshinov.

00:04:17.827 --> 00:04:18.934
in Amshtshinov.

00:04:21.777 --> 00:04:23.138
ver zaynen di mentshn?

00:04:23.582 --> 00:04:26.428
oyf di linke zayt f- shteyedik bin ikh.

00:04:26.890 --> 00:04:28.605
mayn ⟨muter⟩ zitst.

00:04:29.067 --> 00:04:32.537
mayne tsvey shvestern Khane un Rivke

00:04:32.965 --> 00:04:36.131
in di rekhte zayt mayn foter un mayn shvester Leye.

00:04:36.610 --> 00:04:38.916
velkhe iz Leye? zi shteyt?

00:04:38.078 --> 00:04:40.519
Leye, zi shteyt baym tatn, THE BACK.

00:04:40.542 --> 00:04:41.855
in, in, aha.

00:04:41.855 --> 00:04:43.371
ven iz dos genumen gevorn?

00:04:43.410 --> 00:04:44.420
kh'veys nisht.

00:04:44.322 --> 00:04:47.168
umgefar vi alt zayt ir dortn in dem bild?

00:04:46.667 --> 00:04:50.019
ikh bin do geven efsher fuftsn yor.

00:04:49.924 --> 00:04:51.487
un dos iz in Gritse?

00:04:51.207 --> 00:04:52.028
yo.

00:04:54.615 --> 00:04:55.992
ver zaynen di mentshn?

00:04:56.438 --> 00:05:02.079
rekhts iz mayn shvester in mitn, Khane's a man, un dos iz a fraynt ire.

00:05:02.079 --> 00:05:05.257
mayn shvester, di in mitn, iz umgekumen in TREBLINKA.

00:05:07.170 --> 00:05:09.256
ver iz oyf der linker zayt?

00:05:09.381 --> 00:05:10.792
d- der man irer.

00:05:10.292 --> 00:05:11.484
vi heyst er?

00:05:11.507 --> 00:05:12.530
Hershl.

00:05:13.110 --> 00:05:15.618
un dos iz genumen gevorn in velkhn yor?

00:05:15.878 --> 00:05:17.745
UNK in

00:05:18.966 --> 00:05:22.759
in akht un draysikstn yor, far di krig.

00:05:21.852 --> 00:05:23.229
in Gritse?

00:05:22.759 --> 00:05:23.465
ye.

00:05:26.104 --> 00:05:27.566
ver zaynen di mentshn?

00:05:27.623 --> 00:05:29.372
ikh mit mayn man.

00:05:29.513 --> 00:05:30.587
vi heyst er?

00:05:30.424 --> 00:05:31.531
Mendl.

00:05:31.420 --> 00:05:33.084
ven iz dos genumen gevorn?

00:05:32.938 --> 00:05:35.007
ven m'iz gekumen keyn TORONTO.

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:37.388
in akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:05:35.352 --> 00:05:36.358
dos iz i-

00:05:41.882 --> 00:05:43.378
ver zaynen di mentshn?

00:05:42.777 --> 00:05:44.357
nakher der zun

00:05:44.430 --> 00:05:46.162
der kleyner in mitn

00:05:47.113 --> 00:05:48.423
nakher

00:05:48.767 --> 00:05:50.853
bin ikh in blumen kleyd

00:05:52.395 --> 00:05:54.852
un mayn shvester's a shvegerin

00:05:55.281 --> 00:05:56.388
vi heyst zi?

00:05:56.580 --> 00:05:57.873
zi lebt shoyn nisht.

00:05:58.622 --> 00:05:59.645
⟨BARDACH⟩

00:06:01.592 --> 00:06:04.455
un mayn zun, draytsn yor iz er gevorn.

00:06:04.461 --> 00:06:07.543
dos iz er, der, der tsveyter fun lin- fun rekhts?

00:06:05.729 --> 00:06:07.389
MICHAEL.

00:06:07.389 --> 00:06:10.869
der tsveyter fun rekhts, un der ershter iz mayn man.

00:06:08.578 --> 00:06:10.259
oyf der rekhter zayt?

00:06:10.869 --> 00:06:13.019
mit mayn tokhter shteyt derlebn.

00:06:12.983 --> 00:06:16.270
un ver iz di froy in dem bloyen kleyd?

00:06:16.223 --> 00:06:21.701
in broynem kleyd? in bloen kleyt? mayn shvester Rivke vos zi iz geshtorbn.

00:06:17.077 --> 00:06:19.307
in, in bloyen, in bloyen.

00:06:20.695 --> 00:06:21.988
un lebn ir?

00:06:22.078 --> 00:06:24.687
der zun, in di, lebn dem man.

00:06:23.732 --> 00:06:25.498
NO, oyf der linker zayt.

00:06:24.998 --> 00:06:26.125
oyf der linker zayt

00:06:26.125 --> 00:06:28.437
der zu- der zun in mitn

00:06:28.437 --> 00:06:31.506
un der, der man in goln kop iz der man.

00:06:32.288 --> 00:06:33.567
un lebn im?

00:06:33.567 --> 00:06:35.674
lebn dem vaysn tir dortn?

00:06:35.494 --> 00:06:37.250
ikh ken nisht derkenen ver

00:06:37.688 --> 00:06:40.871
un vos iz, dos iz geven dayn, ayer zun's bar mitsve?

00:06:40.323 --> 00:06:42.460
ye, draytsn yor iz er alt geven.

00:06:41.653 --> 00:06:44.684
un dos iz in, in zeks un zekhtsik, yo?

00:06:44.973 --> 00:06:48.023
yo, yo. in TORONTO, alts in TORONTO.

00:06:45.585 --> 00:06:47.047
in TORONTO?

00:06:47.593 --> 00:06:48.836
vu iz dos?

00:06:49.534 --> 00:06:51.451
dos iz in a shul tsi in a hoyz?

00:06:51.441 --> 00:06:52.633
in a hoyz.

00:06:55.373 --> 00:06:56.936
ver zaynen di kinder?

00:06:56.284 --> 00:07:01.340
rekhts iz mayn zun MICHAEL mitn ⟨bukh⟩, un mayn tokhter ZINY.

00:07:01.212 --> 00:07:02.758
in velkhn yor iz dos?

00:07:04.097 --> 00:07:09.946
kh'hob nisht oyfgeshribn oyf di PICTURES. ikh veys, alt geven efsher dray fir yor.

00:07:13.648 --> 00:07:14.739
ver iz dos?

00:07:14.678 --> 00:07:17.186
ma- links mayn tokhter mitn kind

00:07:17.732 --> 00:07:19.413
vi heyst di tokhter?

00:07:18.913 --> 00:07:20.021
ZINY

00:07:19.858 --> 00:07:21.016
un dos kind?

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:22.266
JESSE

00:07:22.525 --> 00:07:23.734
un mayn

00:07:26.085 --> 00:07:27.260
a eydem?

00:07:26.136 --> 00:07:27.986
d- der man, der eydem.

00:07:28.836 --> 00:07:30.129
vi heyst er?

00:07:29.190 --> 00:07:30.078
GARY.

00:07:30.270 --> 00:07:31.985
ven iz dos genumen gevorn?

00:07:32.616 --> 00:07:36.744
iz JESSE alt geven a monat tsvey, tsen yor tsurik.

00:07:36.818 --> 00:07:38.229
in TORONTO?

00:07:37.470 --> 00:07:38.690
yo.

00:08:03.936 --> 00:08:06.309
dos iz MISTE- MISTER MAX BAKER

00:08:14.432 --> 00:08:15.371
OKAY?

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:18.172
fun THE RIGHT, THAT'S MY HUSBAND.

00:08:18.988 --> 00:08:20.129
vi heyst er?

00:08:20.997 --> 00:08:23.370
MAX BAKER

00:08:24.135 --> 00:08:28.280
THAT'S MINE GRANDCHILD JESSE KIRSHENBAUM.

00:08:29.991 --> 00:08:32.415
THIS IS MINE OTHER GRANDCHILD

00:08:32.792 --> 00:08:34.037
SARAH

00:08:34.037 --> 00:08:35.316
KIRSHENBAUM

00:08:35.491 --> 00:08:37.640
THAT'S MINE DAUGHTER, ZINY

00:08:37.640 --> 00:08:38.661
KIRSHENBAUM.
